OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening although a little rain
OL,7,Fspreading to northern Argyll later.
OL,8,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,9,Fcloudy with occasional rain extending
OL,10,Fsouth.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FPatchy rain at first.
OL,13,FOtherwise dry and rather cloudy, some
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine developing in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Further patchy light rain
OL,16,Fspreads southeast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
