OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading southeast on Saturday.
OL,8,FMainly dry with just the odd shower on
OL,9,FSunday. Dry start Monday, rain from
OL,10,Fthe west later.
